1
00:00:00,004 --> 00:01:10,004
( Watch on www.kissasia.co, .club, .be, .org, .net, .id, .xyz )

2
00:02:15,688 --> 00:02:17,272
I’m not your enemy,

3
00:02:17,297 --> 00:02:19,341
I'm here to help.

4
00:02:19,550 --> 00:02:22,594
Do you think everything is as it seems?

5
00:02:23,554 --> 00:02:26,390
Don’t hug anyone too tightly.

6
00:02:28,094 --> 00:02:30,179
Before you realize it...

7
00:02:31,683 --> 00:02:33,268
you’re already bleeding.

8
00:02:41,447 --> 00:02:42,447
Moral?

9
00:02:44,283 --> 00:02:45,951
Does this school still have morals?

10
00:02:46,869 --> 00:02:48,412
Watch your language, Ace.

11
00:02:49,455 --> 00:02:51,165
You may be the Supremo

12
00:02:51,748 --> 00:02:54,709
but I am the headmistress of this school.

13
00:02:55,242 --> 00:02:57,286
As the new SSG Secretary.

14
00:02:58,787 --> 00:03:00,330
How many times do I have to tell you

15
00:03:00,331 --> 00:03:02,166
that I'm not interested in that position?

16
00:03:05,377 --> 00:03:06,377
Listen, Zein.

17
00:03:06,795 --> 00:03:08,005
I'm a detective

18
00:03:08,631 --> 00:03:10,841
at the same time, secret agent.

19
00:03:11,383 --> 00:03:14,345
I can't give you any information.

20
00:03:15,346 --> 00:03:16,346
Zein...

21
00:03:16,597 --> 00:03:17,973
you can be a big asset

22
00:03:19,433 --> 00:03:21,518
if you accept Ace’s offer.

23
00:03:25,689 --> 00:03:27,733
And where do you think you're going?

24
00:03:30,110 --> 00:03:31,110
The restroom...

25
00:03:31,362 --> 00:03:32,404
to change.

26
00:03:32,738 --> 00:03:33,738
No.

27
00:03:34,740 --> 00:03:35,740
Change here.

28
00:03:36,742 --> 00:03:39,453
I said move and get out of my sight.

29
00:03:41,455 --> 00:03:42,735
You're catching on pretty quick.

30
00:03:44,041 --> 00:03:45,041
I like that.

31
00:05:20,095 --> 00:05:23,265
I still think Fritzy
should take the seat.

32
00:05:23,474 --> 00:05:24,516
She's earned it.

33
00:05:26,769 --> 00:05:29,813
The new SSG Secretary is here.

34
00:05:31,064 --> 00:05:33,442
Why is that girl here?

35
00:05:33,984 --> 00:05:36,445
And why is she
wearing my uniform?

36
00:05:38,530 --> 00:05:39,573
Get out of your chair.

37
00:05:39,782 --> 00:05:40,949
President Ace.

38
00:05:41,074 --> 00:05:43,368
Fritzy is still
the SSG Secretary.

39
00:05:43,952 --> 00:05:44,952
All of you

40
00:05:45,412 --> 00:05:46,747
take my command.

41
00:05:48,707 --> 00:05:49,833
And you...

42
00:05:50,667 --> 00:05:53,629
get out of my sight,
Ms. Fritzy Saldivar.

43
00:05:54,171 --> 00:05:56,215
You're no longer
allowed to wear that uniform.

44
00:06:04,932 --> 00:06:05,932
Bitch.

45
00:06:07,684 --> 00:06:08,893
From now on.

46
00:06:08,894 --> 00:06:11,979
Ms. Zein Shion is
the new secretary of HU.

47
00:06:11,980 --> 00:06:13,272
And I no longer want to hear

48
00:06:13,273 --> 00:06:16,401
any complaints
or questions about it.

49
00:06:16,568 --> 00:06:19,196
Respect her like you respect me.

50
00:06:19,571 --> 00:06:20,864
Maybe you're forgetting

51
00:06:21,448 --> 00:06:23,909
that she's in the
top nine of the highest ten.

52
00:06:25,244 --> 00:06:28,205
It may be low in comparison
to your position, Mr. Ty

53
00:06:28,705 --> 00:06:32,251
but you should
respect her because I said so.

54
00:06:33,293 --> 00:06:35,170
And Zein

55
00:06:35,811 --> 00:06:37,731
now that you're part of the council

56
00:06:37,856 --> 00:06:39,566
you have but one responsibility

57
00:06:39,691 --> 00:06:41,276
and that's to stay present with me

58
00:06:41,386 --> 00:06:42,471
or at the office.

59
00:06:42,998 --> 00:06:44,207
No questions asked.

60
00:06:45,013 --> 00:06:46,181
What do you mean?

61
00:06:46,598 --> 00:06:48,350
I- can't say no!?

62
00:06:52,980 --> 00:06:54,690
Music is structure.

63
00:06:55,607 --> 00:06:56,607
Order.

64
00:06:57,484 --> 00:06:59,945
Carefully arranged notes

65
00:07:00,153 --> 00:07:03,240
all in service of a higher purpose.

66
00:07:03,490 --> 00:07:05,993
That is why you learn music here.

67
00:07:06,201 --> 00:07:11,497
If anything that will bolster
your weak, feeble minds.

68
00:07:11,498 --> 00:07:16,168
The kind of minds
that end up late in class.

69
00:07:16,169 --> 00:07:17,838
Right, Ms. Shion?

70
00:07:18,922 --> 00:07:20,382
Find a seat, Ms. Shion.

71
00:07:20,799 --> 00:07:22,843
Surely you can do at least that.

72
00:07:26,471 --> 00:07:28,807
Where are your music sheets?

73
00:07:29,349 --> 00:07:31,059
It's okay ma'am. We can share.

74
00:07:32,853 --> 00:07:33,936
Hopefully, that will be

75
00:07:33,937 --> 00:07:36,398
the last interruption this class will have.

76
00:07:36,815 --> 00:07:38,609
You have your music sheets.

77
00:07:38,942 --> 00:07:42,696
Today, we are learning
vision fugitive.

78
00:07:43,322 --> 00:07:45,908
Follow the tune
of the metronome.

79
00:07:47,242 --> 00:07:48,493
Let's begin.

80
00:08:01,465 --> 00:08:02,633
Replaced?

81
00:08:03,258 --> 00:08:04,635
Just like that?

82
00:08:05,218 --> 00:08:07,804
It's like I didn't do
anything as his secretary.

83
00:08:10,182 --> 00:08:11,642
Don't let it get to you

84
00:08:12,684 --> 00:08:15,062
you're still one of the
big dogs in Hell U.

85
00:08:16,146 --> 00:08:19,107
Just adapt to the situation
and play your cards right.

86
00:08:19,858 --> 00:08:21,735
Don't let this put
you down, Fritzy.

87
00:08:22,569 --> 00:08:23,569
Fine

88
00:08:24,488 --> 00:08:26,323
but she'll regret this.

89
00:08:27,157 --> 00:08:29,117
I'll make sure of it.

90
00:08:36,708 --> 00:08:37,793
Need some help?

91
00:08:38,543 --> 00:08:39,543
Oh my god.

92
00:08:40,087 --> 00:08:41,421
I'd appreciate that.

93
00:08:42,422 --> 00:08:43,422
Sorry

94
00:08:44,383 --> 00:08:46,510
you've been saving my
ass since earlier.

95
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:47,803
Hold on.

96
00:08:57,604 --> 00:08:59,398
Wow, you're so good at that!

97
00:09:01,233 --> 00:09:03,068
I just practice a lot.

98
00:09:10,033 --> 00:09:11,033
I appreciate this,

99
00:09:11,034 --> 00:09:14,037
I hope you tuning this
won't be in vain.

100
00:09:15,372 --> 00:09:16,707
I didn't catch your name.

101
00:09:17,249 --> 00:09:19,042
My name is Nazzer Lumia.

102
00:09:27,676 --> 00:09:28,969
Is there a problem?

103
00:09:31,138 --> 00:09:33,223
You're the leader of
the Black Blood Gang?

104
00:09:35,058 --> 00:09:36,727
I am, my lady.

105
00:09:39,146 --> 00:09:42,983
Don't take anything
you see in face value.

106
00:09:44,443 --> 00:09:48,488
You should be wary
of people's intentions.

107
00:09:48,947 --> 00:09:50,107
Because when the facade breaks

108
00:09:51,283 --> 00:09:54,453
they can be worse than demons.

109
00:10:02,127 --> 00:10:03,670
Number nine, huh?

110
00:10:04,337 --> 00:10:05,797
That's impressive.

111
00:10:11,011 --> 00:10:13,262
But your life doesn't hold value to us

112
00:10:13,263 --> 00:10:14,805
or the rest of the people here.

113
00:10:15,586 --> 00:10:17,379
You're going to die soon.

114
00:10:17,976 --> 00:10:20,687
I'll make you an offer, hmm?

115
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:24,357
There's nothing
that you have that I want.

116
00:10:26,568 --> 00:10:29,154
Calling it an offer was a courtesy...

117
00:10:29,654 --> 00:10:31,281
join us or die.

118
00:10:33,033 --> 00:10:34,367
Be one of us

119
00:10:35,043 --> 00:10:37,545
and I will protect you.

120
00:10:39,206 --> 00:10:40,373
I don't want to.

121
00:10:41,166 --> 00:10:42,375
What a waste.

122
00:10:42,918 --> 00:10:44,377
I can kill you now.

123
00:10:44,711 --> 00:10:45,921
You'll die soon.

124
00:10:46,755 --> 00:10:47,755
Hmm?

125
00:10:51,051 --> 00:10:52,427
Kill me, then.

126
00:10:56,196 --> 00:10:57,823
They're right about you

127
00:10:59,017 --> 00:11:01,603
you are not afraid of death.

128
00:11:02,521 --> 00:11:04,815
The grim reaper
might be afraid of you.

129
00:11:07,567 --> 00:11:09,361
But you won't die yet

130
00:11:10,529 --> 00:11:12,364
we can still use you.

131
00:11:14,616 --> 00:11:16,534
What did I tell you, Paulo?

132
00:11:16,535 --> 00:11:18,870
He likes to hangout here.

133
00:11:21,039 --> 00:11:22,874
Didn't I tell you

134
00:11:24,251 --> 00:11:25,627
if you talk to my girl again

135
00:11:26,002 --> 00:11:27,379
you're a dead man.

136
00:11:28,552 --> 00:11:30,304
She wasn't complaining about it.

137
00:11:31,007 --> 00:11:32,342
Is he being serious, bro?

138
00:11:33,051 --> 00:11:34,594
You think you're brave, huh?

139
00:11:36,555 --> 00:11:37,722
Come on, stand up!

140
00:11:41,643 --> 00:11:43,145
Not so brave now, huh?

141
00:11:43,937 --> 00:11:44,937
Use this!

142
00:11:54,739 --> 00:11:56,366
Stop it!

143
00:11:57,576 --> 00:11:58,576
Hey

144
00:11:59,202 --> 00:12:00,871
it's the Supreme Secretary.

145
00:12:01,257 --> 00:12:02,967
Our apologies, my lady.

146
00:12:03,665 --> 00:12:06,459
This guy has been talking
to my friend's girl.

147
00:12:07,586 --> 00:12:09,212
We just want him
to learn a lesson

148
00:12:09,713 --> 00:12:12,048
like what you guys do in
that council, right?

149
00:12:14,259 --> 00:12:16,928
My lady, don't let him affect you.

150
00:12:16,965 --> 00:12:17,966
He's worthless.

151
00:12:18,763 --> 00:12:19,890
Why did you stop?

152
00:12:20,599 --> 00:12:22,266
Listen to them, my lady.

153
00:12:22,291 --> 00:12:24,501
Let them release their anger. Shit!

154
00:12:24,686 --> 00:12:26,288
Where's your bravery now?

155
00:12:26,313 --> 00:12:27,313
Huh?

156
00:12:29,274 --> 00:12:30,525
I'll kill you!

157
00:12:35,455 --> 00:12:37,875
Are they done with him yet?

158
00:12:38,410 --> 00:12:39,494
Doesn't look like it.

159
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:42,620
This is so boring.

160
00:12:44,706 --> 00:12:46,333
Aren’t you going to help him?

161
00:12:48,168 --> 00:12:50,670
Aren't you one of his underlings?

162
00:12:53,632 --> 00:12:54,632
Help him?

163
00:12:55,417 --> 00:12:57,044
You're funny, aren't you?

164
00:12:57,844 --> 00:12:59,471
Miss Secretary!

165
00:13:00,764 --> 00:13:01,764
I can't help him

166
00:13:05,060 --> 00:13:06,060
but

167
00:13:07,062 --> 00:13:09,147
you see those three guys?

168
00:13:09,814 --> 00:13:13,641
They'll be the next ones to die here.

169
00:13:27,290 --> 00:13:29,250
I think there's chocolate in it

170
00:13:29,251 --> 00:13:31,503
I think so. Is that
alright? I think its better -

171
00:13:33,004 --> 00:13:34,004
Let's go.

172
00:13:35,131 --> 00:13:36,299
She's not done eating.

173
00:13:37,133 --> 00:13:38,260
Haven't she informed you?

174
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:40,428
Fine, let me.

175
00:13:41,304 --> 00:13:43,265
As the new SSG Secretary.

176
00:13:43,473 --> 00:13:45,557
Zein is not allowed
to talk or be with you

177
00:13:45,558 --> 00:13:46,935
unless I allow her.

178
00:13:47,185 --> 00:13:48,436
That's crazy.

179
00:13:48,937 --> 00:13:49,956
Why would you make her do that?

180
00:13:49,980 --> 00:13:51,835
Because she has responsibilities.

181
00:13:52,649 --> 00:13:53,649
Now

182
00:13:53,817 --> 00:13:54,985
if you'll excuse us.

183
00:13:55,902 --> 00:13:56,902
Miss Shion.

184
00:13:57,028 --> 00:13:58,028
Let's go.

185
00:13:58,280 --> 00:13:59,280
Matt.

186
00:13:59,572 --> 00:14:01,700
She isn't done eating yet, is she?

187
00:14:02,367 --> 00:14:03,367
Matt...

188
00:14:05,036 --> 00:14:06,413
Sorry guys.

189
00:14:38,374 --> 00:14:40,125
Sorry, Supremo.

190
00:14:43,116 --> 00:14:44,116
Name?

191
00:14:48,163 --> 00:14:49,163
Name!?

192
00:14:49,672 --> 00:14:51,883
F-Ferry Marcos.

193
00:14:58,631 --> 00:14:59,758
SSG!

194
00:15:07,265 --> 00:15:08,265
Follow me.

195
00:15:13,813 --> 00:15:14,856
The Dark Hell Jail

196
00:15:15,357 --> 00:15:16,483
is waiting for you.

197
00:15:18,294 --> 00:15:19,294
Zein...

198
00:15:19,459 --> 00:15:20,459
Zein!

199
00:15:21,863 --> 00:15:22,947
Excuse me!

200
00:15:33,458 --> 00:15:34,834
If I were you, Zein.

201
00:15:35,335 --> 00:15:37,130
I'd step aside from your position.

202
00:15:37,396 --> 00:15:41,234
You won't like it when
he shows his true colors.

203
00:15:42,342 --> 00:15:43,551
I'm not afraid.

204
00:15:44,386 --> 00:15:45,678
Really now?

205
00:15:46,471 --> 00:15:49,036
I'm honest enough
to admit that I am.

206
00:15:50,115 --> 00:15:52,708
I've witnessed his anger

207
00:15:53,103 --> 00:15:54,771
his demonic anger

208
00:15:55,355 --> 00:15:57,145
and if you see that for yourself

209
00:15:57,482 --> 00:15:59,234
you'd be scared too.

210
00:16:01,319 --> 00:16:02,654
I don't want to die yet.

211
00:16:03,386 --> 00:16:04,929
Please, I don't want to die.

212
00:16:05,490 --> 00:16:07,450
Supremo's word is law.

213
00:16:08,076 --> 00:16:09,077
It's final.

214
00:16:12,247 --> 00:16:13,247
Supremo.

215
00:16:13,498 --> 00:16:15,266
Supremo... I don't want to die yet.

216
00:16:15,291 --> 00:16:16,291
Stop resisting.

217
00:16:16,584 --> 00:16:17,836
I'm begging you.

218
00:16:18,703 --> 00:16:19,504
Faster!

219
00:16:19,504 --> 00:16:20,397
Supremo

220
00:16:20,422 --> 00:16:22,007
I don't want to die yet...

221
00:16:32,767 --> 00:16:35,186
Don't make me push you inside.

222
00:16:41,366 --> 00:16:42,909
I know you, Supremo.

223
00:16:43,736 --> 00:16:45,530
I know your secret.

224
00:16:47,449 --> 00:16:48,449
I know.

225
00:16:49,367 --> 00:16:50,952
That's why I brought you here.

226
00:16:52,036 --> 00:16:53,371
I know your secret too.

227
00:16:55,582 --> 00:16:56,916
How did you find out?

228
00:16:58,710 --> 00:17:00,295
Do you think I
would stoop so low

229
00:17:01,254 --> 00:17:02,505
that I'll bring you here

230
00:17:02,964 --> 00:17:04,549
because you spilled juice on me?

231
00:17:05,758 --> 00:17:07,010
I know your secret

232
00:17:09,220 --> 00:17:10,597
you killed Grace.

233
00:17:12,056 --> 00:17:14,309
And you're scared
that if Jane finds out...

234
00:17:14,642 --> 00:17:16,186
she'll never forgive you.

235
00:17:17,770 --> 00:17:21,316
Grace is the girl whose death
you've witnessed, Zein.

236
00:17:34,704 --> 00:17:36,080
Don't tell her, please!

237
00:17:36,414 --> 00:17:37,414
I won't

238
00:17:38,614 --> 00:17:40,834
if you go to Dark Hell Jail

239
00:17:41,085 --> 00:17:42,337
right now.

240
00:17:54,557 --> 00:17:55,557
Let's go

241
00:17:55,767 --> 00:17:57,644
we still have work
to do for the council.

242
00:18:02,905 --> 00:18:05,210
This is our job, Miss Shion.

243
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:10,239
We need to punish the rule breakers.

244
00:18:10,448 --> 00:18:12,449
Even if that punishment

245
00:18:12,450 --> 00:18:14,452
is death.

246
00:18:22,085 --> 00:18:23,516
Onelski

247
00:18:23,586 --> 00:18:28,174
can you tell the cafeteria staff to
cook the Tuesday special again?

248
00:18:28,508 --> 00:18:30,009
It's so delicious.

249
00:18:30,593 --> 00:18:31,970
Anything for you, Fritzy.

250
00:18:32,262 --> 00:18:34,639
It's like nothing has happened.

251
00:18:35,186 --> 00:18:36,366
- It's like they just placed
- Supremo can you

252
00:18:36,407 --> 00:18:38,201
- an animal in a cage.
- ask them to change...

253
00:18:38,226 --> 00:18:39,686
the cafeteria decor?

254
00:18:40,812 --> 00:18:44,274
I'm so done with that color.

255
00:18:45,175 --> 00:18:49,262
Now I understand why
everyone is so afraid of them.

256
00:18:49,554 --> 00:18:52,391
Their punishments are lethal.

257
00:18:52,574 --> 00:18:53,616
Let's go.

258
00:18:57,620 --> 00:19:00,290
I don't want to stay any
longer with these demons.

259
00:19:00,498 --> 00:19:03,501
I need to find the hidden laboratory asap!

260
00:19:04,252 --> 00:19:06,212
Supremo! Supremo!

261
00:19:10,891 --> 00:19:12,309
I'm Jane.

262
00:19:13,143 --> 00:19:14,352
I'm Ferry's girlfriend.

263
00:19:14,554 --> 00:19:16,847
Supremo, I'm sorry for the interruption

264
00:19:16,848 --> 00:19:20,243
but maybe we can still talk
about Ferry's punishment?

265
00:19:20,369 --> 00:19:21,369
You're too late.

266
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:36,901
Jane...

267
00:19:39,623 --> 00:19:41,083
Jane, right?

268
00:19:43,583 --> 00:19:44,959
Please calm down.

269
00:19:49,547 --> 00:19:50,548
Number nine?

270
00:19:51,065 --> 00:19:52,150
I'm sorry.

271
00:19:52,175 --> 00:19:53,443
I'm sorry for bothering you.

272
00:19:53,468 --> 00:19:56,763
You're wasting time with the likes of me.

273
00:19:58,431 --> 00:20:00,475
But maybe you can help me?

274
00:20:01,309 --> 00:20:03,226
Maybe you can reason with Supremo

275
00:20:03,227 --> 00:20:05,562
to release Ferry from
the the Dark Hell Jail?

276
00:20:05,563 --> 00:20:06,688
We still have time.

277
00:20:06,689 --> 00:20:07,982
They already took him.

278
00:20:16,527 --> 00:20:18,696
The ones inside already took him.

279
00:20:19,629 --> 00:20:22,708
It's like they weren't human.

280
00:20:24,457 --> 00:20:25,875
Jane, I'm sorry.

281
00:20:26,054 --> 00:20:28,682
